app-role.name: FND_DIAG_ACCESS_DASHBOARD_PRIV
app-role.description: Privilege to access Diagnostics Dashboard from global help menu.. This privilege is available from Roles(s): Application Diagnostics Viewer,Application Diagnostics Regular User,Application Diagnostics Advanced User,Application Diagnostics Administrator

app-role.name: FND_DIAG_ADD_RESULT_TO_INCIDENT_PRIV
app-role.display-name: Add Application Diagnostic Test Results To Incidents
app-role.description: Privilege to add diagnostic test results to application incidents.. This privilege is available from Roles(s): Application Diagnostics Advanced User,Application Diagnostics Administrator

app-role.name: FND_DIAG_ADMINISTRATION_DUTY
app-role.description: Duty role to access Diagnostics Dashboard from global help menu, maintain diagnostic tests, maintain tags and values, select, run and schedule diagnostic runs, review diagnostic test status and reports, add diagnostic test results to application incidents, and maintain diagnostics runs.

app-role.name: FND_DIAG_ADVANCED_USER_DUTY
app-role.description: Duty role to access Diagnostics Dashboard from global help menu, select, run and schedule diagnostic tests, review diagnostic test status and reports, and add diagnostic test results to application incidents.

app-role.name: FND_DIAG_CANCEL_TEST_RUN_ANY_USER_PRIV
app-role.display-name: Cancel Application Diagnostic Test Run Submitted By Any User
app-role.description: Privilege to cancel a test run submitted by any user. This allows an administrator to cancel any run away diagnostic test run.. This privilege is available from Roles(s): Application Diagnostics Administrator

app-role.name: FND_DIAG_CANCEL_TEST_RUN_PRIV
app-role.description: Privilege to cancel a test run submitted from the run test.. This privilege is available from Roles(s): Application Diagnostics Regular User,Application Diagnostics Advanced User,Application Diagnostics Administrator

app-role.name: FND_DIAG_DATA_ADMINISTRATION_DUTY
app-role.description: Duty role to access all Diagnostics test data, tag data, test status and test result data for all tests.

app-role.name: FND_DIAG_DATA_ADVANCED_DUTY
app-role.description: Duty role to access all Diagnostics test data, test status and test result data for all tests.

app-role.name: FND_DIAG_DATA_REGULAR_DUTY
app-role.description: Duty role to access all Diagnostics test data, test status and test result data for all tests.

app-role.name: FND_DIAG_DATA_VIEWER_DUTY
app-role.description: Duty role to access Diagnostics test status and test result data for all test runs.

app-role.name: FND_DIAG_MAINTAIN_TAG_PRIV
app-role.description: Privilege to add diagnostic tags, tag values, remove diagnostic tags, and tag values.. This privilege is available from Roles(s): Application Diagnostics Administrator

app-role.name: FND_DIAG_MAINTAIN_TEST_PRIV
app-role.description: Privilege to register diagnostic tests, assign a tag value to a diagnostic test, and unassign a tag value from a diagnostic test.. This privilege is available from Roles(s): Application Diagnostics Administrator

app-role.name: FND_DIAG_PURGE_TEST_RUN_PRIV
app-role.description: Privilege to purge test runs and associated test reports from the run status.. This privilege is available from Roles(s): Application Diagnostics Administrator

app-role.name: FND_DIAG_REGULAR_USER_DUTY
app-role.description: Duty role to access Diagnostics Dashboard from global help menu, select and run diagnostic tests, review diagnostic test status and reports.

app-role.name: FND_DIAG_RUN_DATA_MAINTENANCE_DUTY
app-role.display-name: Application Diagnostic Run Data Maintenance Duty
app-role.description: Duty role to maintain test runs, including the ability to purge test run and test reports, and cancel runaway test runs submitted by any user. This is an administrator duty.

app-role.name: FND_DIAG_RUN_DIAG_TEST_PRIV
app-role.description: Privilege to schedule diagnostic tests and submit jobs to Enterprise Scheduler Service. This privilege does not allow user to view diagnostic test results.. This privilege is available from Roles(s): Application Diagnostics Advanced User,Application Diagnostics Administrator

app-role.name: FND_DIAG_RUN_ONLINE_ONLY_PRIV
app-role.description: Privilege to enter input parameters and run diagnostic test. This privilege does not allow user to view diagnostic test results.. This privilege is available from Roles(s): Application Diagnostics Regular User,Application Diagnostics Advanced User,Application Diagnostics Administrator

app-role.name: FND_DIAG_SEARCH_TEST_PRIV
app-role.description: Privilege to access Diagnostics home page, search tests by name, search tests by tags, and view test details.. This privilege is available from Roles(s): Application Diagnostics Viewer,Application Diagnostics Regular User,Application Diagnostics Advanced User,Application Diagnostics Administrator

app-role.name: FND_DIAG_TAG_MAINTENANCE_DUTY
app-role.description: Duty role to create new diagnostic tags and tag values, and delete them.

app-role.name: FND_DIAG_TEST_EXECUTION_DUTY
app-role.description: Duty role to select and run diagnostic tests, enter input parameters for diagnostic test runs.

app-role.name: FND_DIAG_TEST_MAINTENANCE_DUTY
app-role.description: Duty role to register diagnostic tests, assign tag value to diagnostic tests, and unassign tag values.

app-role.name: FND_DIAG_TEST_REPORTING_DUTY
app-role.description: Duty role to review diagnostic test run status and test reports.

app-role.name: FND_DIAG_TEST_SCHEDULING_DUTY
app-role.description: Duty role to select, and schedule diagnostic tests, enter input parameters for diagnostic test runs.

app-role.name: FND_DIAG_VIEWER_DUTY
app-role.description: Duty role to access Diagnostics Dashboard from global help menu, and review diagnostic test run status and reports.

app-role.name: FND_DIAG_VIEW_RUN_STATUS_PRIV
app-role.description: Privilege to view diagnostic test execution and diagnostic status.. This privilege is available from Roles(s): Application Diagnostics Viewer,Application Diagnostics Regular User,Application Diagnostics Advanced User,Application Diagnostics Administrator

app-role.name: FND_DIAG_VIEW_TEST_REPORT_PRIV
app-role.description: Privilege to view diagnostic test execution summary and detail reports.. This privilege is available from Roles(s): Application Diagnostics Viewer,Application Diagnostics Regular User,Application Diagnostics Advanced User,Application Diagnostics Administrator

app-role.description: Individual responsible for dealing with different manufacturing practices and processes, and for the research and development of systems, processes, machines, tools and equipment that turn raw material into a product.

app-role.name: ORA_XCC_BUDGET_ANALYST_JOB
app-role.description: Analyzes funds available

app-role.name: ORA_XCC_BUDGET_MANAGER_JOB
app-role.description: Manages one or more control budgets, including relevant setup, budget loading, exception analysis, transactional overrides, and funds available analysis and reporting

app-role.name: ORA_ZBS_SALES_ADMINISTRATOR_JOB
app-role.description: Manages sales department and personnel. Performs ongoing administrative tasks, corrects erroneous data, and customizes the application according to business needs.

app-role.name: ORA_ZBS_SALES_MANAGER_JOB
app-role.description: Manages salespersons within the organization. Generates revenue within a territory, builds pipeline, manages territory forecasts, and assists salespersons in closing deals.

app-role.name: ORA_ZBS_SALES_REPRESENTATIVE_JOB
app-role.description: Represents the business to sell its products. Maintains relationships with customers and contacts, builds pipeline, manages leads and opportunities and performs sales forecasting.

app-role.name: ORA_ZBS_SALES_VP_JOB
app-role.description: Manages sales managers within the organization. Responsible for account planning, territory and quota management, and managing sales forecasts for the territory.

app-role.name: ORA_ZCA_CUSTOMER_RELATIONSHIP_MANAGEMENT_APPLICATION_ADMINISTRATOR_JOB
app-role.description: Individual responsible for customer relationship management application administration. Collaborates with customer relationship management application users to maintain consistent financial application setup, rules, and access.

app-role.name: ORA_ZPM_CHANNEL_ACCOUNT_MANAGER_JOB
app-role.description: Sets the objectives and goals for partners. Works with a partner organization to identify what programs best fit the partner organization and the training that the partner should take to increase skill sets or qualify for programs.

app-role.name: ORA_ZPM_CHANNEL_ADMINISTRATOR_JOB
app-role.description: Executes Oracle Partnership Management setup tasks.

app-role.name: ORA_ZPM_CHANNEL_OPERATIONS_MANAGER_JOB
app-role.description: Maintains and manages partner transactional data.

app-role.name: ORA_ZPM_CHANNEL_PARTNER_PORTAL_ADMINISTRATOR_JOB
app-role.description: Maintains customization of all PRM portal pages, external, internal, and anonymous pages.

app-role.name: ORA_ZPM_CHANNEL_SALES_DIRECTOR_JOB
app-role.description: Supervises channel roles to support partner relationships and transactions.

app-role.name: ORA_ZPM_CHANNEL_SALES_MANAGER_JOB
app-role.description: Manages the indirect sales pipeline by routing leads to partners, reviewing lead registrations, approving or rejecting registrations, and forecasting sales.

app-role.name: ORA_ZX_TAX_ACCOUNTANT_JOB
app-role.description: Prepares and files tax returns and reports for an enterprise, including country, federal, state, and local corporate, payroll, and transaction taxes.

app-role.name: ORA_ZX_TAX_ADMINISTRATOR_JOB
app-role.description: Sets up technical areas and the integration with tax service providers.

app-role.name: ORA_ZX_TAX_MANAGER_JOB
app-role.description: Defines the tax policies and most efficient tax configuration. Sets up relatively stable entities that seldom require updates, such as tax regimes and taxes.

app-role.name: ORA_ZX_TAX_SPECIALIST_JOB
app-role.description: Maintains tax configuration, especially the variable entities that require periodic updates, such as tax rates and tax jurisdictions.

app-role.name: ORA_AP_PAYABLES_INVOICE_IMPORT_SUBMISSION_DUTY
app-role.description: Submits Oracle Fusion Payables invoice import program.

app-role.name: ORA_EGP_ITEM_INQUIRY_DUTY
app-role.description: Queries and views items in the enterprise.

app-role.name: ORA_RCV_SHIPMENT_MANAGEMENT_AS_SUPPLIER_DUTY
app-role.description: Manages inbound shipments, creates and uploads advance shipment notices and advance shipment billing notices.

app-role.name: ORA_EGS_SUPPLIER_PRODUCT_ADMINISTRATOR_JOB
app-role.description: Individual in supplier organization responsible for accessing retailer external portal, and uploading and maintaining supplier product and catalog data with the retailer. This catalog data is for both sell-side as well as buy-side transactions.

app-role.name: ORA_INV_SUPPLIER_INVENTORY_MANAGER_JOB
app-role.description: Individual in a supplier organization responsible for managing inventory process control from beginning to end. Monitors available supplies, materials and products in order to ensure that customers, employees and production have access to the materials they need.
